    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Persons who organize auction sales and prepare catalogs, rooms, and advertisements, but do not conduct the sale itself. Experts historically would announce a description of each lot as it was offered, and worked in tandem with commissaires-priseurs.</Note_Text>
